---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "April 24, 2026";
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy - Upraizo"
  description="Upraizo Privacy Policy. Learn how we protect your data. We are fully GDPR compliant and respect your privacy."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-900/30 border-b border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 rounded-t-3xl">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-black text-red-500 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">Legal & Compliance</h2>
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 font-medium">
        Last updated: {lastUpdated}
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="space-y-16 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium">
        
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            Welcome to Upraizo. We respect your privacy and are deeply committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our website and purchase our courses. We are fully compliant with the <strong>General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)</strong>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">2. Zero Analytics & Tracking</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We believe in absolute digital privacy. Unlike most platforms, <strong>we do not use any analytics tools</strong>, trackers, or invasive cookies on our website. 
          </p>
          <p>
            Your browsing activity on Upraizo is entirely private and is not monitored, recorded, or analyzed by us or any third parties. We don't need to track you to provide high-quality education.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">3. The Data We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We only collect the absolute minimum data required to provide our services to you. Data is only collected when you actively choose to create an account to purchase or access a course. We collect:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 mt-6">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-red-500 shrink-0 mt-1"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
              <span><strong>Name:</strong> To personalize your dashboard and issue your course completion certificates.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-red-500 shrink-0 mt-1"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
              <span><strong>Email Address:</strong> Used as your unique identifier to log in, deliver course access, and send password reset links.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-red-500 shrink-0 mt-1"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
              <span><strong>Password:</strong> Cryptographically hashed and stored securely to authenticate your account. We cannot see your actual password.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">4. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <p>
            Your data is used strictly for the purpose of fulfilling our contract with you (giving you access to the courses you paid for) and managing your account securely. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with any third-party advertisers or marketers. Your data stays with us.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-950/20 border border-indigo-100 dark:border-indigo-900/30">
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-indigo-900 dark:text-indigo-100 mb-6 tracking-tight">5. Your GDPR Rights</h2>
          <p class="mb-6 text-indigo-800 dark:text-indigo-200">
            Under the GDPR, you have complete control over your personal data. You hold the following rights:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-indigo-800/80 dark:text-indigo-200/80">
            <li><strong>Right to Access:</strong> You can request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</li>
            <li><strong>Right to Rectification:</strong> You can request the correction of any inaccurate data.</li>
            <li><strong>Right to Erasure (Right to be Forgotten):</strong> You can request the complete deletion of your account and all associated data from our servers at any time.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">6. Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We implement strict industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information. Your sensitive data is encrypted in transit using secure TLS protocols and protected at rest on our secure servers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">7. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, or if you wish to exercise your GDPR rights to access or delete your data, please contact our support team at:
          </p>
          <a href="mailto:privacy@upraizo.com" class="inline-flex mt-6 px-8 py-4 bg-zinc-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-zinc-900 font-bold rounded-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
            privacy@upraizo.com
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
